\c 2
\s Chiratidzo cherwonzi rwekuyera
\p
\v 1 Zvino ndakasimudza meso angu zvekare, ndokuona, zvino tarira munhu, ane rwonzi rwekuyera muruoko rwake.
\v 2 Zvino ndakati: Unoenda kupi? Iye ndokuti kwandiri: Kunoyera Jerusarema, kuona kuti kufara kwaro chii, uye urefu hwaro chii.
\v 3 Zvino tarira, mutumwa waitaura neni wakabuda, umwe mutumwa ndokubuda kumuchingamidza.
\v 4 Zvino wakati kwaari: Mhanya, taura kujaya iri uchiti: Jerusarema richagarwa semaguta asina masvingo nekuda kweuwandu hwevanhu nezvipfuwo zviri mariri.
\v 5 Nokuti ini, anoreva Jehovha ndichava kwariri rusvingo rwemoto kukomberedza, uye ini ndichava kubwinya mukati maro.
\p
\v 6 Haiwa, haiwa! Zvino tizai mubve munyika yekumaodzanyemba, anoreva Jehovha, nokuti ndakakuparadzirai semhepo ina dzekumatenga, anoreva Jehovha.
\v 7 Haiwa! Ziyoni, pukunyuka, iwe ugere nemukunda weBhabhironi.
\v 8 Nokuti anoreva seizvi Jehovha wehondo: Shure kwekubwinya wakandituma kumarudzi akakupambai, nokuti anokugunzvai imwi anogunzva mboni yeziso rake.
\v 9 Nokuti tarirai, ndichazunza ruoko rwangu pamusoro pavo, vachava chinhu chakapambiwa kuvaranda vavo; zvino muchaziva kuti Jehovha wehondo wakandituma.
\p
\v 10 Imba ufare, iwe mukunda weZiyoni; nokuti tarira, ndinouya, uye ndichagara mukati mako, anoreva Jehovha.
\v 11 Zvino marudzi mazhinji achabatanidzwa kuna Jehovha pazuva iro, uye achava vanhu vangu, uye ndichagara mukati menyu, uye muchaziva kuti Jehovha wehondo wakandituma kwamuri.
\v 12 Zvino Jehovha achagara nhaka yaJudha, mugove wake panyika tsvene, uye achasarudzazve Jerusarema.
\p
\v 13 Nyararai, nyama yese pamberi paJehovha; nokuti wamutswa paugaro hwake utsvene.